</p>
<p>You know what's next: use this above with: <code>$pdo = $this-&gt;getPDO()</code>. Repeat
this in the other spot:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="9a532aa839">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-70" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
